<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_BuildMode_Building_Foundations" s="314590">
  <T n="name">0x267F0520<!--String: "Foundations"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\Foundation_01.png">2f7d0004:00000000:e8b68057cf819b5c</T>
      <T n="text">0xA263CFEC<!--String: "Foundations are found in the Build catalog by clicking on the Foundations sort in the House Portrait."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\Foundation_02.png">2f7d0004:00000000:e8b68057cf819b5f</T>
      <T n="text">0xB9955665<!--String: "To add foundation to your lot, use the Foundation Height Widget. This can be found in the center of a block when selecting it. \n\nAll blocks that are touching the selected block will raise and lower together. You can raise and lower separate non touching blocks independent from one another. Only Blocks of the same foundation height and on the same build level can be connected together. Blocks on different foundation heights and levels will never be able to connect.\n\nPro Tip: When trying to match the height of separate block cluster raise and lower the desired cluster until the blocks of the same height and level highlight white."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\Foundation_03.png">2f7d0004:00000000:e8b68057cf819b5e</T>
      <T n="text">0x41128F4<!--String: "To change the foundation style, choose a style from the catalog and click on the foundation you want to change. The style will apply to all of the foundation for a single Room.\n\nProTip: You can hold shift to only apply the foundation style to one side of a Room."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
